Phoenix/Pumpskin::

"Starstorm!"  Phoenix transforms to bot mode and lands next to the 
injured femme.  Pumpskin catches up and transforms as 
well.  "Pumpskin, go find the other Pred Starstorm was talking about."

The Halloween reject runs off toward Nightviper.

"Well, at least his sense of direction is intact," Phoenix 
muses.  "Starstorm, can you hear me?"
